cs.LG, cs.CR, cs.DS, cs.AI, cs.IT 

This paper deals with stochastic optimization and privacy preservation, which are core topics in machine learning and cryptography. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms). Additionally, the paper involves the use of curriculum learning, which falls under the category of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper also discusses the convergence rate and maximum complexity of the proposed method, which is related to the field of cs.IT (Information Theory).
